{"parentUuid":"aacc247b-75bd-4a5b-934f-ae0bcc6af408","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"b57da2ca-b6c6-46a3-a226-31b9c8256309","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"数据库无法直接读写，但根据日志，你的配置现状已经很清楚了。让我直接给你结论和操作步骤。\n\n---\n\n## 当前状态\n\n日志明确显示：你正在用 `DeepSeek-v4-pro`（**没有 `[1m]` 后缀**），这意味着 Claude Code 默认假设该模型的上下文窗口只有约 200K，会提前触发压缩。\n\n```\n[Claude] >>> 请求 URL: https://api.deepseek.com/anthropic/v1/messages?beta=true (model=DeepSeek-v4-pro)\n```\n\n## 视频博主的说法：正确\n\ncc-Switch 支持 `[1m]` 后缀。当你在模型名称后加 `[1m]`，cc-Switch 会告诉 Claude Code 该模型支持 1M token 上下文，从而不会提前压缩。cc-Switch 发送给 DeepSeek API 时会自动剥离 `[1m]`。\n\n## 操作步骤\n\ncc-Switch 是 GUI 程序，你需要手动操作：\n\n1. **打开 cc-Switch 界面**（系统托盘图标，右键 → 打开设置）\n2. 进入**模型供应商（Provider）管理**，找到你正在用的 DeepSeek Provider\n3. 把模型名从 `DeepSeek-v4-pro` 改为 **`DeepSeek-v4-pro[1m]`**\n4. 保存，重启 Claude Code 终端\n5. 终端输入 `/context` 验证，确认显示为 1M 上下文\n\n如果你也用到 `deepseek-v4-flash`，同样加 `[1m]`，Flash 版也原生支持 100 万。\n\n---\n\n要我帮你验证一下 cc-Switch 里具体哪个 provider 需要改吗？我可以看看有没有其他能直接配置的方式（比如通过 cc-Switch 的 localhost API）。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":149,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":73344,"output_tokens":702,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"a1e0fcf0-c8f1-432d-ba65-c85dc4d11d83","timestamp":"2026-04-29T04:14:45.375Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"D:\\ClaudeWorkspace","sessionId":"07a593cf-bcb9-4bf9-a969-effe2aaab829","version":"2.1.121","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
