{"parentUuid":"1b45ea9b-9789-4e41-acf1-60f5de324075","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"437ed935-7cfb-4ab7-9d11-220d35facc75","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"你在回复什么\" (What are you replying?). They're confused because the `/context` output shows 200K still, and my previous message was cut off or confused.\n\nLet me be direct: the `[1m]` suffix and env vars didn't work. The context is still 200K. The `[1m]` trick might work for Claude Code when it talks directly to Anthropic API or for Claude Desktop, but it doesn't work through cc-Switch's proxy.\n\nThe real solution is likely something cc-Switch needs to handle on its side - either a newer version of cc-Switch, or a different configuration approach.\n\nLet me be honest with the user: the `[1m]` trick didn't work with their setup, and this is likely a cc-Switch limitation.","signature":"437ed935-7cfb-4ab7-9d11-220d35facc75"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8117,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":86784,"output_tokens":360,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"201256bb-b55d-4c4b-92ff-8201b9c578d9","timestamp":"2026-04-29T04:33:39.105Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\ClaudeWorkspace","sessionId":"07a593cf-bcb9-4bf9-a969-effe2aaab829","version":"2.1.123","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"parentUuid":"201256bb-b55d-4c4b-92ff-8201b9c578d9","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"437ed935-7cfb-4ab7-9d11-220d35facc75","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"结论很清楚：**`[1m]` 后缀在你的 cc-Switch 上不生效。**\n\n两轮验证：加了 `[1m]`、重启了 cc-Switch、加了环境变量，`/context` 还是纹丝不动的 **200K**。\n\n视频博主说的 `[1m]` 可能对某些版本的 cc-Switch 有效，但至少你这版（通过日志看模型名直接带 `[1m]` 转发给了 DeepSeek API 而不是被 cc-Switch 解析处理）**不管用**。\n\n本质原因：Claude Code 的上下文窗口大小是由代理层（cc-Switch）在协议握手阶段上报的，你这边 cc-Switch 并没有因为 `[1m]` 后缀就改变上报值。这个得等 cc-Switch 更新或者换个支持自定义上下文窗口的代理方案（比如 LiteLLM）。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8117,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":86784,"output_tokens":360,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"18c944f7-d267-44fa-9def-3dad0f876311","timestamp":"2026-04-29T04:33:44.844Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\ClaudeWorkspace","sessionId":"07a593cf-bcb9-4bf9-a969-effe2aaab829","version":"2.1.123","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
