{"parentUuid":"c8265162-95bd-498e-bc24-1d7f4f0d68d8","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"93b3f3d3-c039-4516-abdc-106b3c8b1b7e","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_02_UKirNh4vrYF6S2ifD2Eedcbj","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"cc-switch github farion1231 context window 1m model configuration advanced settings\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"cc-switch/docs/user-manual/en/README.md at main · farion1231/cc-switch\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/blob/main/docs/user-manual/en/README.md\"},{\"title\":\"windows下安装和配置claude code、cc-switch、skill、mcp\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnblogs.com/L1nssv-diary/p/19778643\"},{\"title\":\"cc-switch/docs/user-manual/zh/3-extensions/3.1-mcp.md at main · farion1231/cc-switch\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/blob/main/docs/user-manual/zh/3-extensions/3.1-mcp.md\"},{\"title\":\"一款适用于 Claude Code、Codex 和 Gemini CLI 的跨平台桌面全能助手工具(开源)\",\"url\":\"https://routerpark.com/zh/proxy/%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%BE%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E-claude-code-codex-%E5%92%8C-gemini-cli-%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%A8%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%85%A8%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7-%E5%BC%80%E6%BA%90-1768274247167\"},{\"title\":\"cc-switch/docs/release-notes/v3.12.3-zh.md at main · farion1231/cc-switch\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/blob/main/docs/release-notes/v3.12.3-zh.md\"},{\"title\":\"CC Switch 完整安装部署与云模型接入配置教程\",\"url\":\"https://gitcode.csdn.net/69df421b0a2f6a37c59fdf3d.html\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Code / Codex / Gemini CLI 全方位辅助工具\",\"url\":\"https://docs.packyapi.com/docs/ccswitch/1-common.html\"},{\"title\":\"CC-Switch使用教程\",\"url\":\"https://docs.packyapi.com/docs/ccswitch/\"},{\"title\":\"CC Switch - SiliconFlow\",\"url\":\"https://docs.siliconflow.cn/cn/usercases/use-siliconcloud-in-ccswitch\"},{\"title\":\"CC Switch - API易文档中心\",\"url\":\"https://docs.apiyi.com/en/scenarios/programming/cc-switch\"}]\n\n## Search Results Summary\n\nHere's what I found regarding **cc-switch** by **farion1231** (Jason Young), specifically around the **1M context window** and **advanced model configuration**:\n\n---\n\n### Repository\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch\n- **License**: MIT\n- **Latest version**: v3.12.3+ (as of March 2026)\n- **Stack**: Tauri 2 + React + Rust — cross-platform (Windows / macOS / Linux)\n\n---\n\n### Codex 1M Context Window (v3.12.3)\n\nThis is the specific feature you're looking for. As documented in the [v3.12.3 release notes](https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/blob/main/docs/release-notes/v3.12.3-zh.md), CC Switch includes a **Codex 1M context window toggle** in its config editor:\n\n- **Checkbox** sets `model_context_window = 1000000` in Codex's `config.toml`\n- **Auto-fills** `model_auto_compact_token_limit = 900000` when enabled\n- **Clean removal** of both fields when disabled\n\nThis allows you to extend Codex CLI's default context window to 1 million tokens with a single click from the GUI.\n\n---\n\n### Other Advanced Configuration Features\n\n| Feature | Description |\n|---|---|\n| **Model Slot Mapping** | Map Claude Code's haiku/sonnet/opus slots to different models per provider |\n| **Reasoning Effort Mapping** (v3.12.3) | Cross-provider reasoning intensity control |\n| **DISABLE_AUTOUPDATER** | Toggle to prevent Claude Code auto-upgrades |\n| **Tool Search Toggle** (v3.12.3) | `ENABLE_TOOL_SEARCH` env var for Claude 2.1.76+ |\n| **Failover & Circuit Breaker** | Multi-provider queue with auto fallback and health checks |\n| **Custom JSON Config** | Advanced provider config via raw JSON (e.g., `ANTHROPIC_MODEL` override) |\n| **Model Test / Health Check** | Latency testing and model connectivity verification |\n\n---\n\n### How to Access These Settings\n\n1. Open CC Switch → click a provider → **Edit** (or the config editor)\n2. Look for the **\"Codex 1M Context Window\"** checkbox in the advanced/config section\n3. You can also inject custom JSON config per provider (e.g., for third-party models like MiniMax-M2.5 via Aliyun marketplace using `\"ANTHROPIC_MODEL\": \"MiniMax-M2.5\"`)\n4. CLI commands are also available: `cc-switch --app codex config common show` / `config common set --json '{...}' --apply`\n\n---\n\n### Relevant Links\n\n| Resource | URL |\n|---|---|\n| Docs Index | https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/tree/main/docs |\n| User Manual (EN) | https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/blob/main/docs/user-manual/en/README.md |\n| v3.12.3 Release Notes (ZH) | https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/blob/main/docs/release-notes/v3.12.3-zh.md |\n| Releases | https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/releases |\n| Installation Guide (brew) | `brew tap farion1231/ccswitch && brew install --cask cc-switch` |\n\nWould you like me to dig deeper into any specific aspect, such as the exact `config.toml` format or how to configure the 1M window for other CLI tools beyond Codex?\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"136f5160-bc5d-4e82-925a-9d7fc647f986","timestamp":"2026-04-29T04:37:03.826Z","toolUseResult":{"query":"cc-switch github farion1231 context window 1m model configuration advanced settings","results":[{"tool_use_id":"call_00_49YJmcCi7m7dQETXaXq32Iad","content":[{"title":"cc-switch/docs/user-manual/en/README.md at main · farion1231/cc-switch","url":"https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/blob/main/docs/user-manual/en/README.md"},{"title":"windows下安装和配置claude code、cc-switch、skill、mcp","url":"https://www.cnblogs.com/L1nssv-diary/p/19778643"},{"title":"cc-switch/docs/user-manual/zh/3-extensions/3.1-mcp.md at main · farion1231/cc-switch","url":"https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/blob/main/docs/user-manual/zh/3-extensions/3.1-mcp.md"},{"title":"一款适用于 Claude Code、Codex 和 Gemini CLI 的跨平台桌面全能助手工具(开源)","url":"https://routerpark.com/zh/proxy/%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%BE%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E-claude-code-codex-%E5%92%8C-gemini-cli-%E7%9