areful not to break anything. Let me be conservative and just propose the moves, then execute.\n\nActually, the user wants me to just do it. Let me be practical and organize the mess.\n\nLet me group the loose files:\n\n**Okki project:**\n- check_okki.js → scripts\n- explore_okki.js → scripts\n- launch_okki.js → scripts\n- launch_okki2.js → scripts\n- okki_full.png → screenshots\n- okki_screenshot.png → screenshots\n\n**Rehema project:**\n- read_rehema.js → scripts\n- open_rehema.js → scripts\n\n**Customer investigation (Okki-related):**\n- investigate_customers.js → scripts\n- investigate_email.js → scripts\n- investigate_files.js → scripts\n- investigate_scope.js → scripts\n- find_chat.js → scripts\n- find_chat2.js → scripts\n- read_chat.js → scripts\n- read_chat3.js → scripts\n- scan_all_chats.js → scripts\n- verify_output.js → scripts\n- verify_output2.js → scripts\n\n**General:**\n- compare_invoice.js → likely invoicing, maybe `_tools/`\n- explore_frames.js → web scraping tool, `_tools/`\n\n**Already in 08_客户跟进/ that needs reorganization:**\n- These all seem Okki-related based on the context\n- CHECKPOINT.md → reports\n- *.json → data/\n- *.docx → reports/\n- images/ → merge into screenshots/\n- scripts/ → already there\n- 知识库/ → seems like a reference copy\n\n**My temp files to delete:**\n- find_vault.ps1\n- fix_vault_path.ps1\n\nLet me write a script to do all this organization.","signature":"0e62bd44-e5b1-47e2-b1ef-3aa327958533"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":251,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":137216,"output_tokens":2391,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"71cd56db-ea5d-44fa-8cb3-c2758d836d54","timestamp":"2026-04-29T05:24:40.269Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vs